OL,3,CUnpaid carers tell of exhaustion and
OL,4,Cfrustration with a system in crisis
OL,6,FNew research shows the number of
OL,7,Funpaid carers working more than 35
OL,8,Fhours a week has skyrocketed to 1.9
OL,9,Fmillion people
OL,11,FA rise of 70% in two decades. And
OL,12,Fthere is a crisis of supply and demand
OL,13,Fwhen it comes to getting help.
OL,15,FWhile requests for adult social care
OL,16,Fhave risen 15%, capacity has only gone
OL,17,Fup by 2.5%, leaving the system at
OL,18,Fbreaking point:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
