OL,3,CUnpaid carers tell of exhaustion and
OL,4,Cfrustration with a system in crisis
OL,6,FAbby Jitendra, Author of Institute for
OL,7,FPublic Policy Research report said:
OL,8,F"We're already seeing some of the
OL,9,Fcracks in the system. We know that
OL,10,Fmore and more people are having to be
OL,11,Funpaid carers left with no choice
OL,12,Fbecause the system is too unaffordable.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
