OL,3,CUnpaid carers tell of exhaustion and
OL,4,Cfrustration with a system in crisis
OL,6,F"We need to build support for the
OL,7,Fsystem in the long term, because more
OL,8,Fof us are going to need it, and that
OL,9,Fwork has to start now."
OL,11,FThe government is now looking into how
OL,12,Fit could eventually implement a
OL,13,Fnational care service, similar to the
OL,14,FNHS, but researchers warn against
OL,15,Ftrying to make care free for everyone,
OL,16,Finstead, recommending it be made
OL,17,Faffordable for everyone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
