OL,4,Cfrustration with a system in crisis
OL,6,FAbby Jitendra said: "There are very
OL,7,Ffew or no comparable countries that
OL,8,Fhave completely free social care at
OL,9,Fthe point of use.
OL,11,F"And what we have are some really
OL,12,Fpragmatic models, you know, things
OL,13,Flike free personal care in Scotland,
OL,14,Finsurance based models, where you pay
OL,15,Fa little bit and you get out, such as
OL,16,Fin the Netherlands and Japan.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
