OL,3,CUnpaid carers tell of exhaustion and
OL,4,Cfrustration with a system in crisis
OL,6,F"We've got means tests, like in
OL,7,FAustralia, where you pay what you can
OL,8,Fafford, so there are all these
OL,9,Fexperiments going on abroad that we
OL,10,Fcan learn from and start putting into
OL,11,Fmotion.
OL,13,FThe Department for Health and Social
OL,14,FCare said: "We value the immense
OL,15,Fcontribution of all unpaid carers.
OL,17,FThat's why we have delivered the
OL,18,Fbiggest uplift to the Carer's
OL,19,FAllowance threshold since the 1970s `
OL,20,Fan increase of around #2,000 - and are
OL,21,Freviewing Carer's Leave.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
