OL,6,FThey added "We inherited a social care
OL,7,Fsystem facing significant challenges,
OL,8,Fbut we are turning it around."
OL,10,FBack in Manchester, a sustainable
OL,11,Fsystem is something Susan and John say
OL,12,Fthey desperatley want to see
OL,14,FSo they don't have to worry about
OL,15,Ftheir future.
